
BERZERK:
   Just type berzerk during the fight !

ART:
  The berzerk is the feature of a fighter, fighting with all his 
  power against the opponent. Being berzerk means min 1 up to 3
  extra attacks, depending on your level. If you are berzerk you
  are easier to hit, but you have a better saving throw against 
  hold spells.

COST:
  nothing its a feature
  

  
 
   
